	(509,127,'','','Thai Tan','ANTVR KIT: All-IN-ONE Universal Virtual Reality Kit','antvr-kit','<div></div><p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The ANTVR KIT is an entire virtual reality system that will transport users into their own virtual realities, as they play their favorite games and watch their favorite movies, all in HD, (with 1920x1080/1.03 megapixels per eye). Equipped with a 4:3 standard screen, this kit includes a virtual reality headset that gives users a 100° diagonal field of view, creating a personalized I-MAX type feel. Furthermore, both the headset as well as the remote controller included in this kit come equipped with a 9-axis IMU (Inertial Measurement Unit), which tracks the users head and hand movements for an overall immersive experience. Additionally, the remote controller is able to be used as a gamepad, light saber, gun and even a joystick, making it easy to play almost any game while using this device. Overall, this is a great option for virtual reality gaming and/or viewing, and at only $300, is an affordable option for many who wish to join the virtual world.</span></p><ul><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Totally immerse yourself in any game or movie in either 2D or 3D.</span></li><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">Enjoy an HD display with 1920x1080/1.03 megapixels per eye.</span></li><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Comes with a virtual reality headset, a video driver box, a remote controller and a lithium battery.</span></li></ul>','[{\"key\":\"HD Quality\",\"value\":\"Yes\"},{\"key\":\"Megapixels\",\"value\":\"1920x1080\\/1.03 megapixels per eye\"},{\"key\":\"Viewing\",\"value\":\"2D and 3D\"},{\"key\":\"Comes With\",\"value\":\"a virtual reality headset, a video driver box, a remote controller and a lithium battery.\"},{\"key\":\"Screen\",\"value\":\"4:3 standard screen\"},{\"key\":\"Field of View\",\"value\":\"100\\u00b0 diagonal field of view\"}]',300.00,300.00,7,'https://w