	(510,78,'','','Thai Tan','Enflux Smart Clothing: 3D Workout Tracking and Form Feedback','enflux-smart-clothing','<div></div><p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The Enflux Smart Clothing is smart clothing that you wear as you work out, that will track your form as you work out, progress as a whole, heart rate and more. Enflux then uses Bluetooth to send this information to your phone (via the free app), which translates it into both statistics, motivation and even a virtual model of yourself, which you can use to see how your form looks as you work out, allowing you to make connections were necessary. Furthermore, this device can give you customized work outs all they way from beginner up to advanced, or allows you to set it to freestyle when you want to do your own thing at the gym. Overall, this is a great fitness tracking product that users can look forward to enjoying starting January of 2017.</span></p><ul><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Also includes a heart rate monitor.</span></li><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">Includes 10 embedded motion sensors to track your movement as you exercise. </span></li><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Equipped with an O2 reader.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></span></li></ul>','[{\"key\":\"Sensors\",\"value\":\"10\"},{\"key\":\"Heart Rate Monitor\",\"value\":\"Yes\"},{\"key\":\"O2 Reader\",\"value\":\"Yes\"},{\"key\":\"Tracks movement in\",\"value\":\"arms, legs, and torso\"},{\"key\":\"Connectivity\",\"value\":\"Bluetooth\"}]',499.00,499.00,7,'https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1850884998/enflux-smart-clothing-3d-workout-tracking-and-form/description','','[{\"key\":\"Average\",\"value\":0,\"counter\":\"\"},{\"key\":\"Amazon\",\"value\":0,\"counter\":0}]','0','','','','Active','Best Enflux Smart Clothing Reviews and Deals','The Enflux Smart Clothing is a fitness tracking system users wear, with 10 embedded sensors, a heart rate monitor and O2 reade