	(511,85,'B011U2QYO2','','Thai Tan','Pavlok','pavlok','<div></div><p>Imagine a wearable that could help you reduce food cravings, break bad habits like nail biting or smoking and zaps you awake in the morning when you snooze you alarm twice. Seems impossible? Not with Pavlok -- these are what it exactly does. Pavlok is a wearable which sends vibration, beeps and mild electric stimulus to help you achieve these things. Backed by 80+ of scientific research and with testimonies of real people, Pavlok is achieving what it promises. You don\'t need a smartphone to connect with Pavlok. You just wear it on your wrist.</p><div><br/><ul><li>A wearable designed to help user form healthy habits through powerful commitment techniques</li><li>Uses vibrations, mild electric stimulus and beeps as triggers </li><li>With an alarm that shocks you awake, literally</li><li>Can be used as a standalone wearable, no need to connect with a smartphone</li><li>But to enable smart tracking and app connection, you can connect it to your Android or iOS device</li></ul><br/><p>Almost 80% of the 96 Amazon reviewers have given this wearable a perfect 5 score. They have shared stories of how Pavlok have changed their lives for the better. Overall, Pavlok received a 3.8-star rating.</p></div>','[{\"key\":\"Manufacturer\",\"value\":\"Pavlok\"},{\"key\":\"Model\",\"value\":\"1\"},{\"key\":\"Part Number\",\"value\":\"1\"},{\"key\":\"Color\",\"value\":\"Black\"},{\"key\":\"Product Size\",\"value\":\"0.65 X 1.42 X 1.4 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Package Size\",\"value\":\"3.7 X 6.4 X 6.4 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Weight\",\"value\":\"0.15 Pound\"}]',199.00,199.00,1,'http://www.amazon.com/Behavioral-Technology-Group-1-Pavlok/dp/B011U2QYO2%3Fpsc%3D1%26SubscriptionId%3DAKIAIQYICLTUI4NBTPGA%26tag%3Dideaing07-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB011U2QYO2','','[{\"key\":\"Average\",\"value\":\"0.00\",\"counter\":1},{\"key\":\"Amazon\",\"value\":4,\"counter\":96,\"link\":\"http:\\/\\/www