	(513,129,'B00ECHYTBI','','Thai Tan','Infant Optics DXR-8 Video Baby Monitor With Interchangeable Optical Lens','infant-optics-dxr-8-video-baby-monitor-with-interchangeable-optical-lens','<div></div><p>Infant Optics DXR-8 Video Baby Monitor is the first ever monitor that has an interchangeable set of lens. You can choose from a normal lens, a wide angle lens (sold separately) and zooming lens. With this technology, you are able to choose the most suitable focal length and viewing angle of the room and of your baby that you are monitoring. Use the zooming lens when your baby is sleep at night and swap it with a wide angle one when your baby is up and crawls around. This baby monitor is jampacked with features, making it the #1 Amazon Best Seller in Baby Monitors:</p><div><br/><ul><li>Large 3.5&#34; full-color LCD display with sound-activated LED display</li><li>Remotely controllable pan, tilt, and zoom </li><li>Long battery life of up to 10 hours on power-saving mode</li><li>Equipped with interchangeable lens technology, optical zoom is included, wide angle lens is sold separately</li></ul><br/><p>The Infant Optics Baby Monitor has an average rating of 4.3 stars in Amazon. It\'s an excellent rating so far, considering that the number of reviewers have gone up to 3,367. 69% of those who reviewed gave it a 5-star rating. </p></div>','[{\"key\":\"Manufacturer\",\"value\":\"Infant Optics\"},{\"key\":\"Model\",\"value\":\"DXR-8\"},{\"key\":\"Part Number\",\"value\":\"DXR-8\"},{\"key\":\"Color\",\"value\":\"White\\/Biege\"},{\"key\":\"Product Size\",\"value\":\"3.6 X 8.5 X 9.2 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Package Size\",\"value\":\"3.6 X 8.5 X 9.2 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Weight\",\"value\":\"2.05 Pound\"}]',229.99,170.66,1,'http://www.amazon.com/Infant-Optics-DXR-8-Monitor-Interchangeable/dp/B00ECHYTBI%3FSubscriptionId%3DAKIAIQYICLTUI4NBTPGA%26tag%3Dideaing07-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB00ECHYTBI','','[{\"key\":\"Average\",\"value\":\"3.50\