	(514,129,'B017B2043W','','Thai Tan','Arlo Q - 1080p HD Security Camera with Audio (VMC3040-100NAS)','arlo-q-1080p-hd-security-camera-with-audio','<div></div><p>With the Arlo Q 1080p HD Security Camera, you can see and hear everything in complete clarity. It offers a new sense of security with its HD quality, night vision capabilities and 2-way audio. It also sends you notifications whenever motion or sound is detected in the area that you are monitoring. Arlo can be used in both indoors and outdoors. It\'s weather-proof and wire-free -- no need for wire installation. So, you can choose to place a number of these in your home -- patio, backyard, front and back door, your rooms.</p><p><br/></p><ul><li>Stream in HD quality</li><li>Get alerts when motion or sound is detected</li><li>Guard your home 24/7, even at night with night vision</li><li>24/7 non-stop recording with a backup cloud recording (free for the first 7 days)</li><li>Can be attached using a wall-mount of magnetically</li></ul><p><br/><br/><!--StartFragment--><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);float: none;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span>More than half of the reviewers were impressed with the video quality and easy installation that they gave it a perfect 5-star rating. Overall, it has received a 3.8-star rating from 126 Amazon reviewers. </span><!--EndFragment--><br/><br/><br/></p>','[{\"key\":\"Manufacturer\",\"value\":\"Netgear Inc\"},{\"key\":\"Model\",\"value\":\"VMC3040-100NAS\"},{\"key\":\"Part Number\",\"value\":\"VMC3040-100NAS\"},{\"key\":\"Color\",\"value\":\"White\"},{\"key\":\"Product Size\",\"value\":\"4.93 X 5.99 X 4.45 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Package Size\",\"value\":\"4.6 X 5.1 X 6 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Weight\",\"value\":\" Pound\"}]',219.99,214.95,1,'http://www.amazon.com/Arlo-1080p-Security-Camera-VMC3040-100NAS/dp/B017B2043W%3Fpsc%3D1%26SubscriptionId%3DAKIAIQYICLTUI4NBTPGA%26tag%3Dideaing07-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creativ