	(516,122,'B019OH9898','','Aiza Coronado','iRobot Braava Jet','irobot-braava-jet','<div></div><p>iRobot Braava Jet is iRobot\'s new robot mop that can give a more thorough cleaning than its predecessor. It\'s yet to be released on April 1 on major shopping sites like Amazon, Best Buy, Target and more. But, we thought that you would want to get in on the juicy details before anybody else will be buying them and the stock runs out. Unlike the older Braava, this Braava jet can only cover 20% of what the older version can, but it can give it a thorough cleaning with 3 modes: Wet Mopping, Damp Sweeping and Dry Sweeping. You just need to attach the cleaning pad of your choice and Jet will automatically recognize what type of cleaning you want. It utilizes vibration cleaning, a water nozzle to spray on the area and it also comes with a premixed detergent on the pads. Here are more of its features:</p><ul><li>One power button to signal Jet to start cleaning</li><li>No sensors or navigation, just bumper to detect objects</li><li>Covers 150 to 200 square feet of space</li><li>Easy-to-use and affordable</li></ul>','[]',199.99,191.98,1,'','','[{\"key\":\"Average\",\"value\":\"NaN\",\"counter\":2},{\"key\":\"Amazon\",\"value\":0,\"counter\":0},{\"key\":\"CNET\",\"link\":\"http:\\/\\/www.cnet.com\\/products\\/irobot-braava-jet-240-mopping-robot\\/\",\"counter\":1},{\"key\":\"Engadget\",\"value\":\"\",\"link\":\"http:\\/\\/www.engadget.com\\/2016\\/03\\/15\\/irobot-bravaa-jet\\/#\",\"counter\":1}]','0','','0','','Active','iRobot Braava Jet Reviews and Deals','iRobot Braava Jet is iRobot\'s new robot mop that can give a more thorough cleaning than its predecessor. Ideaing provides aggregated reviews and lowest price on iRobot Braava Jet.','\"\"','April 2016','2016-03-15 07:32:01','2016-05-14 07:57:22'),
	(517,129,'','','Thai Tan','Rebecca Smart Shoot-Intelligent Shooting Robot','rebecca-smart-shoot-intelligent-shooting-robot','<div></div><p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The Smart Shoot-Intelligent Shooting Robot is a robot that has been specially designed to take the highest quality photos, all while hands free, freeing the user up to be a part of all the memories themselves and not just be stuck as the one behind the camera. Equipped with face recognition technology, (both for a single person as well a group photos), as well as intelligent tracking, (which allows the robot to track moving subjects for a dynamic video), this robot is truly one of a kind, being the first in its class to offer such high quality picture and technology for such an affordable price. Furthermore, this camera is extremely easy to both install and use, making it a great solution for anyone -- tech savvy or not.</span></p><ul><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Hands free</span></li><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">Equipped with face recognition.</span></li><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Also equipped with intelligent tracking.</span></li></ul>','[{\"key\":\"Face Recognition\",\"value\":\"Yes\"},{\"key\":\"Intelligent Tracking\",\"value\":\"Yes\"},{\"key\":\"Hands Free\",\"value\":\"Yes\"},{\"key\":\"Installation\",\"value\":\"3 steps\"},{\"key\":\"Remote Control Included\",\"value\":\"Yes\"}]',0.00,0.00,7,'https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1544031815/smart-shoot-intelligent-shooting-robot','','[{\"key\":\"Average\",\"value\":0,\"counter\":\"\"},{\"key\":\"Amazon\",\"value\":0,\"counter\":0}]','0','','','','Active','Best Smart Shoot-Intelligent Shooting Robot Reviews and Deals','The Smart Shoot-Intelligent Shooting Robot is a hands free photo taking device. Ideaing provides aggregated reviews and lowest price on the Smart Shoot-Intelligent Shooting Robot.','\"\"','','2016-03-15 14:30:28','2016-03-19 15:56:23'),
