	(574,85,'','','Thai Tan','LUXES Bracelet','luxes-bracelet','<div></div><p>Are you fond of staying under the sun? You should have this Luxes bracelet. It is a bracelet that indicates your UV exposure and help you prevent sunburn, wrinkles and most importantly, skin cancer. The silicon-based material darkens in color when it detects UV radiation. What you do is apply sunscreen on both the bracelet and your skin. When the Luxes bracelet starts to darken, it\'s time for you to re-apply your sunscreen. The Luxes is waterproof and works under water, which is great because you can enjoy the beach without having to worry if you are having too much UV radiation or not. It also works in freezing temperature. Fresh snow is a good reflector of UV. So, you still need to use sunscreen even though, or rather, especially during winter. Snow doubles the UV exposure!</p><div><br/><ul><li>Changes color when exposed to UV -- this is your alert to re apply sunscreen</li><li>Waterproof and will work under water</li><li>Still suitable for use even in freezing temperature</li><li>No battery required</li></ul><p><br/></p></div>','[]',0.00,0.00,13,'http://the-luxes.com/','','[{\"key\":\"Average\",\"value\":\"NaN\",\"counter\":1},{\"key\":\"Amazon\",\"value\":0,\"counter\":0},{\"key\":\"Luxes\",\"link\":\"http:\\/\\/the-luxes.com\\/\",\"counter\":1}]','0','','','','Active','LUXES Bracelet Reviews and Deals','LUXES Bracelet is an ultraviolet radiation monitor to indicate your UV exposure and help you prevent sun burn, wrinkles and skin cancer. Ideaing provides aggregated reviews and lowest price on LUXES Bracelet.','\"\"','','2016-03-20 03:23:31','2016-04-02 19:01:23'),
