	(626,148,'','','Thai Tan','SmartPlate: Instantly analyze everything you eat!','smart-plate','<div></div><p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The SmartPlate is a new way to keep track of the calories you are consuming, without having to manually write down or enter information into your journal or phone. Working with 99% accuracy, the SmartPlate uses small cameras to identify the food you are eating -- even it is a prepared meal with mixed ingredients -- and is able to weight the food on your plate to determine portion sizes and calorie amounts. Then, after the plate has determined what you are eating, as well as how much, it sends that information, (with calorie amounts) to your smart phone, allowing you to easily keep track of your calories consumed for the day. Furthermore, this entire process only takes about a second. Overall this is an incredibly fun product that will surely change the entire game of counting calories itself, and is available for order now.</span></p><ul><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Instantly transfers all the information on your meal to the free SmartPlate app.</span></li><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">Weighs and identifies food with 99% accuracy.<br/></span></li><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Compatible with iOS and Android devices.</span></li></ul>','[{\"key\":\"accuracy\",\"value\":\"99%\"},{\"key\":\"Weighs up to\",\"value\":\"1500 grams\"},{\"key\":\"Compatibility\",\"value\":\"iOS and Android\"},{\"key\":\"Microwavable\",\"value\":\"No\"}]',149.00,149.00,7,'https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1816678675/smartplate-instantly-track-and-analyze-everything','','[{\"key\":\"Average\",\"value\":0,\"counter\":\"\"},{\"key\":\"Amazon\",\"value\":0,\"counter\":0}]','0','','0','','Active','Best SmartPlate Reviews and Deals','The SmartPlate recognizes what the users is eating, weights it, determins nutritional value and uploads information to app. Ideaing provides aggregated re