	(941,44,'','','Thai Tan','Ingrein Smart Clock','ingrein-smart-clock','<p>The Ingrain Smart Clock is a smart clock that has been designed to fit beautifully into any home and help the user disconnect from their smart phones when with family or friends, (or even just catching up on some much needed personal time), while resting assured that they will be notified of anything important that happens in the meantime. In fact, the Ingrain Smart Clock is compatible with over 100 commonly used smart phone apps, and allows users to customize various alerts with their corresponding color notifications — the back of the clock lighting to display a ring of color around the clock when a notification occurs. Furthermore, the Ingrain Smart Clock will always display current/upcoming temperatures as well as traffic information so users are never surprised before leaving the home or office again.  All of this while also coming equipped with motion sensors, allowing the Ingrain Smart Clock to detect unexpected motion and then send an SMS alert and/or trigger other various smart home security devices. Really a great device featuring and incredibly chic design of repurposed wood, the Ingrained Smart Clock is sure to help disconnect when desired, while resting assured you will remain in the loop of important activity and goings on. The Ingrain Smart Clock receives 4 out of 5 stars by the editors of Gadget Flow and will be available to consumers in Spring of this year (2016). </p><ul><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Receive notifications via customizable light settings from all your most important apps.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></span></li><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">Always see the current/upcoming weather and traffic so you are never surprised before leaving your home/office again.<br/></span></span></li><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Equipped with motion detec