	(1058,128,'B00KZHP102','','Aiza Coronado','D-Link DCH-S150 Wi-Fi Smart Motion Sensor','d-link-dch-s150-wi-fi-smart-motion-sensor','<div></div><p>You shouldn\'t be just alerted whenever your motion sensor detects suspicious motion. Your devices should be smart and react to certain scenarios. This D-Link Smart Motion Sensor is one. It can connect with any IFTTT-compatible product or app so you can assign certain functions that leans in towards your safety, convenience, and fancy preferences. For example, when motion is detected during the night, you can set your porch lights to turn on. Or if you open your door after a night out, the hallway lights will turn on and your favorite music will play. Cool, huh?</p><p><br/></p><ul><li>Detects motion up to 26 feet with a sensor angle of 100-degree horizontally and 80-degree vertically</li><li>Receive push notifications via mobile app</li><li>Connect to your existing WiFi network</li><li>Pair with other IFTTT enable product</li></ul><p><br/></p><p>Amazon customer reviewers were pretty pleased with the product. One user said that it has a very reliable alert system and is contented with the security system that he built. The overall rating is quite low because the previous app can\'t send notifications, but since the update, users are happy with the sensor and they have increased their star review ratings.</p>','[{\"key\":\"Manufacturer\",\"value\":\"D-Link Systems, Inc.\"},{\"key\":\"Model\",\"value\":\"DCH-S150\"},{\"key\":\"Part Number\",\"value\":\"DCH-S150\"},{\"key\":\"Color\",\"value\":\"White\"},{\"key\":\"Product Size\",\"value\":\"2 X 2 X 2.25 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Package Size\",\"value\":\"3 X 4.8 X 6.4 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Weight\",\"value\":\"0.13 Pound\"}]',39.99,34.99,1,'http://www.amazon.com/D-Link-DCH-S150-Wi-Fi-Motion-Sensor/dp/B00KZHP102%3FSubscriptionId%3DAKIAIQYICLTUI4NBTPGA%26tag%3Dideaing07-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB00KZHP102','','[{\"key\":\"Average\",\"val