	(1061,116,'B0167HG1V6','','Aiza Coronado','ASUS RT-AC5300 Wireless AC5300 Tri-Band Gigabit Router, AiProtection with Trend Micro for Complete Network Security','asus-rt-ac5300-wireless-ac5300-tri-band-gigabit-router','<div></div><p>Meet the world\'s first Gigabit router with built-in game accelerator, widest Wi-Fi coverage, and tri-band Smart Connect plus an AiProtection with Trend Micro for a totally complete network security. Having one is like having 3 wireless routers at once because it has a dual 5GHz wireless band and a single 2.4GHz wireless band. Enjoy lag-free online gaming, uninterrupted 4k video streaming, and quick downloads of large files simultaneously. </p><p><br/></p><ul><li>Tri-band with a dual 5GHz, and a single 2.4GHz</li><li>Armed with the latest 802.11ac 4x4 technology for maximum throughput </li><li>Wi-Fi coverage of up to 5,000 sq. ft.</li><li>Supports multiple compatible clients to connect</li></ul><p><br/></p><p>Almost 3/4 of the Amazon customer reviewers have awarded this game-changing router with a perfect 5. Most of them had owned different routers in the past, but this one has the most reach, is the most stable, and is the fastest. Even an IT professional has given it a perfect 5.</p>','[{\"key\":\"Manufacturer\",\"value\":\"ASUS Computer International Direct\"},{\"key\":\"Model\",\"value\":\"RT-AC5300\"},{\"key\":\"Part Number\",\"value\":\"RT-AC5300\"},{\"key\":\"Color\",\"value\":\"\"},{\"key\":\"Product Size\",\"value\":\"24.5 X 6.5 X 24.5 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Package Size\",\"value\":\"4.9 X 11.4 X 14.1 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Weight\",\"value\":\"3.21 Pound\"}]',399.99,429.00,1,'http://www.amazon.com/RT-AC5300-Wireless-Tri-Band-AiProtection-Complete/dp/B0167HG1V6%3Fpsc%3D1%26SubscriptionId%3DAKIAIQYICLTUI4NBTPGA%26tag%3Dideaing07-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB0167HG1V6','','[{\"key\":\"Average\",\"value\":\"4.00\",\"counter\":1},{\"key\":\"Amazon\",\"value\":4.5,\"counter\":251,\"link\":\"htt